OL,3,CJersey's Chief Minister looks to delay
OL,4,Ckey living wage pledge
OL,6,FJersey's Chief Minister wants to push
OL,7,Fback bringing in the living wage,
OL,8,Fdelaying one of the key targets he
OL,9,Fmade when he came into power.
OL,11,FDeputy Lyndon Farnham's hope to shift
OL,12,Fits proposed introduction from January
OL,13,Fto April 2025 has been made off the
OL,14,Fback of significant pressure from
OL,15,Flocal businesses.
